  "remarks": "\nFormer Member of the Committee on Science, Education and Culture of the Federation Council of the Russian Federation. His duties as a Member of the Council of the Russian Federation ended in September 2017. He is currently a member of the parliament of North Ossetia.  On 1 March 2014, Totoonov publicly supported in the Federation Council the deployment of Russian forces in Ukraine.  \n The trust services sanctions were imposed on 21/03/2023.",
